{
  "texts": [
    "In all experiments, τ c was set to 1U where U stands for the concrete unit such as ms or μs.",
    "Note that although the choice of units in simulations can be arbitrary, it becomes a critical parameter for a hardware implementation.",
    "Moreover, hyperparameter γ = 10 ensures that even for higher values of initial learning rate the neurons, which are active in the equivalent ReLU network, generate a spike in the interval ½t ðnÞ min, t ðnÞ max Þ.",
    "The simulation results were averaged across 16 trials.",
    "The batch size was set to 8."
  ]
}